Package: win11-window-tiling-kde
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: dbus-x11 | dbus, bash, plasma-workspace, kwin-wayland | kwin-x11
Maintainer: Local Build <local@localhost>
Description: Windows 11-style window tiling for Debian KDE Plasma
 Installs and configures the KZones KWin script for zone-based window
 snapping and Windows 11-style Super+Arrow keyboard shortcuts.
 .
 Built specifically for Debian with KDE Plasma 6. After install, run
 'win11-tiling-setup' and log out and back in.
